content: 2007 年举办了第一届比利时 X-Qlusive，一年后举办了第一届比利时唯一的 Q-dance 节：The Qontinent。比利时的活动由安特卫普的 Q-dance 办公室组织。
contentEn: In 2007 the first Belgian X-Qlusive was organized and a year later the very first Belgian only Q-dance festival was organized: The Qontinent. The events in Belgium are organized by the Q-dance office in Antwerp.
